{
  "id": "adv_card_ngs_11_02",
  "title": "伊吹渚 2話 湿度がないと",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_lesson-01-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "s1",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0.7
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "（あれから数日……渚はレッスンスタジオで毎日）\n（ライバルキャラの演技を練習しているようだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（A few days later… Nagisa is in the lesson studio every day）\n（practicing her performance as the rival character…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs001.m4a",
      "text": "お弁当作ってきたよ、大好物の生姜焼き入れてみたの\n隠し味の山椒とオイスターソースも入ってるから",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I made you a lunch box‚ with your favorite ginger pork\nI added Japanese pepper and oyster sauce as secret ingredients",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 14.1730607986,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs002.m4a",
      "text": "貴方のお母さんが作るものと全く同じレシピだよ\nぜーったい口に合うはずだから……え？　教えてない？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It's the exact same recipe your mother uses\nI'm suuuure you'll like it… Eh? You didn't tell me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 24.3063941319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs003.m4a",
      "text": "聞いてないよ？　じゃあなんで知ってるのかって？\nコウタ君のことならなんでも知ってるわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You didn't tell me? Then why do I know?\nI know everything when it comes to you‚ Kota",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 40.1063941319,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs004.m4a",
      "text": "それぐらい、当然でしょ……？\nふふふ……コウタ君のこと大好きなんだから……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That much is only natural‚ right…?\nHehehe… Because I love you so much‚ Kota…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 43.2900002163,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "（お、恐ろしい……目が据わってるぞ渚……）\n（なぜそこまで演じられるのに自信なさげだったんだ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（S-Scary… Her eyes are dead‚ Nagisa…）\n（How could she play it so well yet have no confidence?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 56.1000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs005.m4a",
      "text": "ふぅ……あ、{user}さん！\n様子を見に来てくれたんですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Phew… Oh‚ {user}!\nDid you come to see how I'm doing?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 63.8385270754,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ……良かった、いつもの渚に戻ってくれた……\nさっきまで別人のような表情だったから驚いたよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah… Thank goodness‚ the usual Nagisa is back…\nI was surprised because you had a completely different expression until now…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 70.6000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "その様子だと、もうライバル役の演技は完璧だな\n少しだけ心配していたが杞憂だったよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Looking at that‚ your performance as the rival is perfect\nI was a bit worried‚ but it was unnecessary",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 79.0333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs006.m4a",
      "text": "そう言ってもらえるのは嬉しいんですが……\nまだまだ全然納得がいかないんです",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I'm happy you say so‚ but…\nI'm still not satisfied with it at all",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 85.6725624719,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs007.m4a",
      "text": "特にさっきのシーンなんて\nもっともっと愛情たっぷりの方がいいと思うんです……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Especially in that scene just now\nI think it would be better with much‚ much more affection…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.1058958052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs008.m4a",
      "text": "今のままだと、恩着せがましく、押しつけがましい……\n暴走の割合が高過ぎるのかな……ううん、違う……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "As it is‚ it feels patronizing and pushy…\nIs the ratio of \"going out of control\" too high?… No…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 100.9058958052,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs009.m4a",
      "text": "その要素も、もちろん必要だから……\nだからこそ、湿度がないと……うーん、でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Because that element is also necessary…\nThat's why‚ without more \"humidity\"… Hmm‚ but…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 112.1392291385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "し、湿度……？　湿度ってなんだ……？\n俺が理解出来ない高度な次元で悩んでいるのか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-Humidity…? What do you mean by humidity…?\nIs she agonizing on a higher level that I can't understand…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 123.1333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "演技の経験はそこまでないはずなのに\nまさかここまで分析して没頭出来るとはな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "She shouldn't have much acting experience‚\nyet she can analyze and immerse herself to this extent…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 130.1666684468,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs010.m4a",
      "text": "あ、{user}さんはどう思いますか？\n今みたいに迫られたとしたら",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oh‚ what do you think‚ {user}?\nIf someone approached you like I just did",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.4049655912,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "お、俺か？　……すまない、そんな経験がないから\nなんとも言えないというか……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "M-Me? …Sorry‚ I don't have experience with that‚\nso it's hard to say anything…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 144.5000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs011.m4a",
      "text": "だったら……そうですね……\n違うシーンをやってみるので、感想をいただけますか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If that's the case… I see…\nI'll try a different scene‚ could you give me your thoughts?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 151.3333351135,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、もちろん\nそれだったら協力出来そうだ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ of course\nI think I can help with that",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 157.4000017802,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs012.m4a",
      "text": "じゃあ、デート中にはぐれて一人になったコウタ君の\n前にアリサちゃんが突然現れて迫るシーンをやりますね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then‚ I'll do the scene where Arisa suddenly appears\nand approaches Kota who's become alone after getting lost",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 162.8832414783,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "（もうそのあらすじを聞いてるだけで怖いんだが……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Just hearing the synopsis is scary enough…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.7425353053,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs013.m4a",
      "text": "もう大丈夫。寂しかったよね、ほら、手握ってあげる\n私がずっと一緒だから安心してほしいな……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You're safe now. You were lonely‚ right? Here‚ I'll hold your hand\nI'll be with you forever‚ so I want you to feel safe…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 179.221358887,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs014.m4a",
      "text": "ずっと、ずっと……ずっと一緒だよ？\n貴方を一人にするあの女は……いらない……！！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Forever‚ ever… we'll be together forever‚ okay?\nThat woman who leaves you alone… isn't needed…!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 194.2213649905,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "（こ、言葉が出てこない……）\n（まるで心臓を鷲掴みにされたような重圧だ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（W-Words won't come out…）\n（It's a pressure like my heart is being gripped…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 203.9333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs015.m4a",
      "text": "ど、どうでしょうか……？\n{user}さん？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "H-How was it…?\n{user}?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 210.2333391825,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-koh011.m4a",
      "text": "す、すまない、演技に見入ってしまっていた\nその調子なら素晴らしい演技が出来ると思うぞ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "S-Sorry‚ I was captivated by your acting\nWith that momentum‚ you'll be able to give a wonderful performance…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 216.1688746456,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02/sud_vo_adv_card_ngs_11_02-ngs016.m4a",
      "text": "わぁ、ありがとうございます！\nこの方向でもう少しだけ練習してみます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Wow‚ thank you so much!\nI'll practice a bit more in this direction!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 223.0409089243,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "speakerNameEn": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――撮影初日",
      "translations": {
        "en": "――First day of filming",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 226.95340004,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.15340004
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_tokyopark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "tokyopark-00-noon",
      "startTime": 228.15340004
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "ngs",
      "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
      "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
